  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A strange phone call has invaded the peace of Grandpa… Only you have the power to rescue the mistress so Grandpa can return to chill in his house. The neighborhood is now your fight arena for an epic fight to rescue the mistress, kill all the enemies with unpredictable yet full of puzzles environments. Can you rescue the mistress?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967320/extras/0c9f4bec848668bd451b1f773e78f775.poster.avif?t=1762356899\" width=676 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967320/extras/0c9f4bec848668bd451b1f773e78f775.webm?t=1762356899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967320/extras/0c9f4bec848668bd451b1f773e78f775.mp4?t=1762356899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Campaign</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grandpa will have a visually stunning retro third-person action-adventure campaign that will keep you on the edge of your seat, with semi open linear level environments with very good world-building and storytelling. Grandpa will have intensely gratifying gameplay experience blending Retro graphics with modern third person mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967320/extras/f9cf6a08fde92907b1a1efd672eb6fad.poster.avif?t=1762356899\" width=676 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967320/extras/f9cf6a08fde92907b1a1efd672eb6fad.webm?t=1762356899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967320/extras/f9cf6a08fde92907b1a1efd672eb6fad.mp4?t=1762356899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><strong>Fight for saving the mistress</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle a relentless enemy through retro levels and challenging </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >boss fights to continue to move the story foward. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
